{"tid":555263,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"遊生個台原來又拆撚咗夥","createTime":"2018-02-09T09:13:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-09T12:26:06.000Z","uid":8588,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b325c7c7f38c38542dc2e59360e29a99103cdf99","tid":555263,"uid":8588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T09:13:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/09/171251_bb9d9513ff93a334db96b2ba21dfb483.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F09%2F171251_bb9d9513ff93a334db96b2ba21dfb483.png&h=13efd492&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n曾幾何時&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n有班友仔，響某個頻道，為世界各地足球作出客觀嘅評述同分析。星球無啦啦受到破壞，班友仔就當然星散四方啦。<br />\n<br />\n今日，班友仔準備要重聚再講波啦，無論你識波唔識波，識得我哋嘅，唔係唔嚟睇呀嘛？<br />\n<br />\n今晚題目：<br />\n熱刺插水爭議、<br />\n熱刺肥仔球迷有幾識波、<br />\nVR技術運用、<br />\n北倫敦打比賽前分析、<br />\n曼聯仲有得爭冠。<br />\n<br />\n今晚直播主持：沙比<br />\n開波時間：2月9日，晚上11時<br />\n<br />\n期間將有星球人亂入，York，阿蟲......仲有你哋應該會識嘅，想知邊個打邊個，入嚟睇直播啦。"},{"pid":"0608b5526e992a5d0024007164630abbcc583836","tid":555263,"uid":5600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T09:23:57.000Z","msg":"沙比同阿松兩個漏口既一齊講波應該聽撚死人"},{"pid":"e6d1771fff3caa8c8df1486030f4f82a0a49e0f2","tid":555263,"uid":8588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0608b5526e992a5d0024007164630abbcc583836","tid":555263,"uid":5600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T09:23:57.000Z","msg":"沙比同阿松兩個漏口既一齊講波應該聽撚死人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T09:25:32.000Z","msg":"好似話啊Nick今晚都會上去講"},{"pid":"c09eb46f85cd1cdb2a820dbf5b540180bcb3e92c","tid":555263,"uid":12984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T09:56:10.000Z","msg":"樂仔歸邊面"},{"pid":"6771b0aa32fb2a9e73292d91b6dd17fcf324760f","tid":555263,"uid":8588,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c09eb46f85cd1cdb2a820dbf5b540180bcb3e92c","tid":555263,"uid":12984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018